 @D_GMZ_IV  If you're still having trouble with it, here's how I resolved it: 

I deleted the desktop app and reinstalled it. I actually did this about 3 times. The time it finally worked was when it asked me to do 2FA via the ChatGPT app on my iPhone.

Sounds random, I know, not sure how/why it's like this. But it's finally working.
